      "role": "user",
      "content": "it’s just so quiet here. work, sleep, repeat. sometimes i look at my reflection and i don’t even recognize the person looking back. it feels like i’m just a ghost haunting my own apartment. i do all these things, i send these emails, i buy this food, but it feels like none of it actually matters. like i’m not even really here.",
